p://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2854921542897145e-17, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0532045575929363e-21, \"text\": \"Durant\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kevin_Durant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was Durant who shone the brightest for the mighty Americans in their opening win versus Serbia last Sunday, July 28, as the three-time Olympic gold medalist went off for a game-high 23 points on a near-perfect 8-of-9 shooting.\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 2108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1970, \"end\": 1976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999675546866, \"rank\": 3.241770781043716e-08, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 35-year-old Durant showed no signs of rust in his return, scattering 21 of his 23 points in just the first two quarters on a spotless 8-of-8 field goal clip.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"James, likewise, came to play for USA, posting all-around numbers of 21 points, 7 rebounds, and 9 assists in his first Olympic appearance since the 2012 London Games.\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2273, \"end\": 2278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2854921542897145e-17, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"