e men's basketball Olympics.\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2586, \"end\": 2600, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demographics_of_South_Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9410865448215554, \"rank\": 0.06260152746043211, \"text\": \"South Sudanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demographics_of_South_Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Demographics_of_South_Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pitted against a powerhouse USA squad filled with NBA superstars, look for former NBA two-way guard Carlik Jones to lead the charge for South Sudan as they look to pull off one of the biggest upsets in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.6364286240820218, \"rank\": 0.570804641202384, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2724, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.304466512604044e-18, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2756, \"end\": 2759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.304466512604044e-18, \"text\": \"NBA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Basketball_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2774, \"end\": 2786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlik_Jones\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlik Jones\", \"types\": [